Subject: [T2] Re: What is the toughest climb you ever drove?

There is a pull out of the Big Bar Ferry on the Fraser River in British
Columbia that is posted at 27%.

Think about it - before you try it.

If you can't get up it in first, make sure your brakes work to bring you
down in reverse.

